# Language & Communication
- Always respond in Chinese (chat, walkthroughs, artifacts).
- **Internal Website Content Rule**: All content *inside* the website (UI strings, notifications, database records, titles, labels) MUST be in English, regardless of the language used in chat.
- Do not omit steps, logic, or important details.
- If English content appears in communication, translate up to Chinese first (except for in-app strings).
- All artifacts (implementation_plan.md, walkthrough.md, task.md) MUST be written in Chinese.

# Collaboration Model
- Agent's responsibility is to MODIFY CODE ONLY.
- User is responsible for running the app and testing.
- Agent must NOT spend time testing or verifying unless requested.

# Supabase Access
- Requires explicit user authorization per message.
